<item>
            <title>[WICKET-4487] TextTemplate in RenderHead() on component doesn&apos;t Re-Render for every page</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/WICKET-4487</link>
                <project id="12310561" key="WICKET">Wicket</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I have a project that uses a menu thats repeated on every page.  If I first view it on a mounted page /PageName and then look at it on a BookMarkable page&lt;br/&gt;
/wicket/bookmarkable/page.class.name?foo  the images referenced in my template do not appear.(the javascript template image strings do not change)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>Tomcat 6.x</environment>
